Plex version RC2
=================

Plex is a small, fast, and scalable application framework,
with its own high performance webserver.

This is the second release candidate of Plex.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  HTTP::HeaderParser::XS
  Moose
  MooseX::Types
  CSS::Minifier::XS
  JavaScript::Minifier::XS
  File::MMagic
  Path::Abstract

